            "id": 73199,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Создай переменную <code>activeUsers</code>, которая хранит массив со значением <code>\"Finn\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" activeUsers = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;Finn&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"];\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Active:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(activeUsers);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"28\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Larry&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Active:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"[ 'Finn' ]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>activeUsers</code>, затем <code>[</code>, а затем <code>\"Finn\"</code>, <code>]</code>.</p></body></html>"
